<div class="govuk-width-container">
  <main class="govuk-main-wrapper govuk-main-wrapper--l" id="main-content" role="main">
    <div class="govuk-grid-row">
      <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
        <div class="govuk-panel govuk-panel--confirmation">
          <h1 class="govuk-panel__title">
            Application complete
          </h1>
          <div class="govuk-panel__body">
            Your reference number is <br><strong><%= @app_reference %></strong>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="govuk-body">
          We have sent you a confirmation email.
        </p>

        <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">What happens next</h2>

        <p class="govuk-body">
          We've sent your application to your local council.
        </p>

        <p class="govuk-body">
          They will contact you for more information and undertake some safety and criminal checks before granting you with the certificate you need to sponsor a child's visa.
        </p>

        <p class="govuk-body">
          Read guidance on sponsoring a child from Ukraine for more information on what checks will be made to ensure you can sponsor a child.
        </p>

        <p class="govuk-body">
          If you are granted a certificate, that will only be eligible for sponsoring the child mentioned in your application. If you would like to sponsor more than one child, even if they are related,
          <%= govuk_link_to 'complete another application', '/sponsor-a-child' %>.
        </p>

      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</div>
